ncxmms2 is an ncurses xmms2 client. The aim of this project is to write ncmpcpp
like client for xmms2. 

For customization see ncxmms2.conf and ncxmms2.colors.

Currently supported features:
 - Base features:
   - Display playback status
   - Playback control
   
 - Screens:
  - Help
  - Active playlist
  - Local file system browser
  - Medialib browser
  - Playlists browser
  - Equalizer
  
Hotkeys:
 Screens switching:
  Help : 1
  Active playlist : 2
  Local file system browser : 3
  Medialib browser : 5
  Playlists browser : 6
  Equalizer : 7
  
 Playback control:
  Toggle : P
  Stop : s
  Next : >
  Prev : <
  Seek forward : f
  Seek backward : b

 List view:
  Move cursor up : up arrow
  Move cursor down : down arrow
  Move cursor to the first item : Home
  Move cursor to the last item : End
  Toggle selection : insert
  Invert selection : *
  Select items by regular expression : +
  Unselect items by regular expression : \
  Jump to next selected item : .
  Jump to previous selected item : ,
  
 Playlists browser:
  Create new playlist : n
  Remove playlist : Delete
  Rename playlist : r
  Go to currently active playlist : o
  
 Playlist window:
  Clear playlist : c
  Shuffle playlist : S
  Go to currently playing song : o
  Add file / directory : Ctrl+O
  Add url : Ctrl+U
  Show song info : i
  
 Local file system browser:
  Add file or directory to active playlist : space
  Add file to active playlist : enter
  Go up : left arrow
  Change directory : g
  Reload directory : R
 
  Medialib browser:
   Refresh : R
   Add artist / album / song to active playlist: space, enter
   Show song info : i
  
